      "rationale": "Pump geometry derived from manufacturer CAD files (revision B, released 2025-10-14). Boundary conditions (inlet flow rate, outlet pressure, rotational speed) sourced from the primary experimental dataset (https://uofa.net/morrison/data/fda-pump-piv-2025; dataVintage 2025-10-08). The model underwent a turbulence-model coefficient recalibration on 2025-11-03 (modelRevisionDate); the assessment team determined this update did not alter the boundary-condition inputs or geometry, and therefore the pre-revision dataset remains applicable without re-extraction. No formal re-validation of input traceability was performed following the revision. Blood viscosity set to 0.0035 Pa·s; density 1060 kg/m³, consistent with bench-test fluid characterization."
