    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The primary experimental dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-08) predates the model revision (2025-11-03) by 26 days; the assessment team reviewed the revision change log and concluded that the turbulence-model coefficient update affects only internal solver parameters and does not invalidate the boundary-condition or geometry inputs sourced from the dataset. This determination was made by engineering judgment without a formal re-validation exercise. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met across all 5 operating points. The model is accepted for the stated COU.",
